name: FURRY SEX: Cabaret 💋🔞
description:
Furry Sex: Cabaret is a casual puzzle game. Solve the puzzle and discover the girls' stories.
Your goal is to connect at least 4 cells with the same number to create a bigger number and reach the level's goal.
Features: 6 characters to explore
20+ puzzle levels
interesting story
All Characters are over the age of 18
